  "text": "• Rheumatoid arthritis: Dry mouth, pruritus and paresthesia are frequent complaints in patients with rheumatoid arthritis [CITATION_1] . Rheumatoid cervical myelopathy causes paresthesia in the arms and neck pain [CITATION_2] .",
